Class RegistrationApplication

java.lang.Object
BTO_Management_System.RegistrationApplication
public class RegistrationApplication extends Object
Represents an application submitted by an HDBOfficer to register for handling a specific BTOProject. This record tracks the officer, the project of interest, and the current status of the registration.
